## Acceptance Criteria

- [x] `burnt.advise(job_id="...")` fetches metrics from `system.lakeflow.job_run_timeline`
- [x] Returns `AdvisoryReport` with aggregated metrics from multiple runs
- [x] Includes variability analysis for autoscaling recommendations
- [x] Uses worst-case metrics (max spill, peak memory) for safe sizing
- [x] Provides confidence boost indicator: "High confidence from 5 runs"
- [x] Graceful error when job not found or no runs available
- [x] Unit tests cover: job metric aggregation, variability calculation, error cases
- [x] Integration with existing `advise()` function structure

