## Implementation

### Changes Made
- `src/burnt/core/models.py` - Added `AggregatedMetrics` model
- `src/burnt/advisor/session.py` - Implemented `_fetch_metrics_from_job()`, `_advise_from_job()`, `_calculate_confidence()`, `_generate_job_insights()`
- `src/burnt/advisor/report.py` - Added `num_runs_analyzed` and `confidence_level` fields to `AdvisoryReport`
- `src/burnt/cli/main.py` - Added `--job-id` option to `advise` command
- `tests/unit/test_advisor.py` - Added tests for job ID analysis

### Implementation Notes
- Uses `TableRegistry.lakeflow_job_run_timeline` for enterprise support
- Aggregation: max() for memory (safety), avg() for duration
- Variability calculated as std dev / mean percentage
- Confidence: low (1 run), medium (2-4 runs), high (5+ runs)
- CLI displays confidence level after analysis

